text: There is an unnecessary blank space at the top of the markdown in the plan sidebar

proposedTasks.title: Fix blank space at top of Plan sidebar markdown
proposedTasks.description: The Plan sidebar renders markdown with an unnecessary blank space at the top of the content area. Investigate the markdown source and rendering pipeline for Plan files displayed in the sidebar (PRD 7.2.4). The root cause is likely either: (a) the Plan markdown content includes a leading newline or whitespace that isn't trimmed before rendering, or (b) the markdown renderer/container has excess top padding/margin. Acceptance criteria: (1) Plan markdown in the sidebar renders with no spurious blank space above the first visible content line. (2) Fix applies to all Plan files, not just a specific one. (3) No regression in markdown styling or layout elsewhere in the sidebar.

taskTitles: Fix blank space at top of Plan sidebar markdown
